@startuml LoginEnsure
skinparam backgroundColor #121212
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #8AB4F8
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #444444
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #1E1E1E
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #E8EAED

actor User as U
participant "NextAuth client" as App
participant "/api/drive/ensure" as API
participant "Google Drive API" as GD
database Dexie as DB
collections "Google OAuth" as GO

U -> App: Open / Sign In
App -> GO: OAuth (openid email profile + drive)
GO --> App: Access token (JWT session)

note over App: On sync or first ensure
App -> API: ensureProjectFolder(projectId,name,driveFolderId?)
API -> GD: Ensure /My Drive/SST
GD --> API: Root folder id
API -> GD: Ensure <ProjectName>__<projectId>
GD --> API: Project folder id
API --> App: {rootId, projectFolderId, movedOrMissing?}
App -> DB: Save/Update driveFolderId
@enduml

